(:title Buddhism Connect: Email Teachings: The energy of depression:)
Summary: Depression can be thought of as a blockage in our energy flow, and sometimes distraction or physical movement can help to relieve it. At other times it is too strong for that, but we can keep working with it, being kind to ourselves, recognizing it as a mental state that will pass.
